{
  "texts": [
    "This scenario raises concerns about the erosion of academic integrity, with educational institutions grappling to detect and address instances of irresponsible GenAI use (Yu, 2023).",
    "Furthermore, it highlights the potential for missed learning opportunities and diminished engagement in collaborative, interactive learning environments (Tlili et al., 2023).",
    "Educators and institutions are prompted to implement stringent policies (Nah et al., 2023), educational campaigns, and technological safeguards to mitigate the negative consequences of this unbridled dependence on GenAI.",
    "The responsible use of GenAI needs to be incorporated into the curriculum to guide students on how to use the technology in an appropriate manner.",
    "Educators need to teach the limitations of GenAI and punish academic dishonesty and unethical practices."
  ]
}